Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.96,0:00:10.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎大人的达尔塔尼亚军方才平安与我军会合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.13,0:00:13.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,另外刚收到消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.05,0:00:17.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,乌尔莉卡大人的舰队即将抵达独角兽城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.85,0:00:18.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的表哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的战斗才刚开始哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.96,0:00:53.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.43,0:01:03.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,北海的征服者 诺尔德的舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜姐姐让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 要开始联合演出咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.24,0:03:19.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么诺尔德的舰队会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.04,0:03:23.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成绕了大陆半圈吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只是士兵的话是可以走过来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.09,0:03:29.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而船只需要在这边造即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.55,0:03:40.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了迄今为止的战斗  我方海军伤亡严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,面对如此大规模的舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.52,0:03:46.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是艾德吉雅阁下的海上宫殿也撑不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都让诺尔德进攻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.36,0:03:51.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德军这次肯定会出击了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被人从海陆一起进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城也撑不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.45,0:04:02.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请问该怎么输呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.79,0:04:06.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可做不出不战而降这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来会做好战斗准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后坐镇城门指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎样告知邻近诸国呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就请他们自行判断吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还得感谢他们迄今为止的协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.89,0:04:23.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为让他们付出众多牺牲而谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那从属君主呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.27,0:04:29.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,命令他们投降的话大概会骂我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会骂您我不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我可不认为他们会乖乖听命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.95,0:04:40.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,具体告知方式就交给劳拉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.12,0:04:46.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就留在这里联系诸国和君主们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.63,0:04:48.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,海尔格 你负责治疗战斗伤员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不必分敌我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这看上去似乎有些矛盾不过这也是战争啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.14,0:05:05.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,二位为公爵尽忠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我由衷感谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您武运昌隆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:17.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,替我转告西露卡 就说你的进言非常正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,其实您早就料到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只是马丽娜手段高明而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,替我给提欧也带个话好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.51,0:05:35.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诺尔德来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有上干艘船的大舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.55,0:05:41.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正乘着海风全速向这边驶来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,约西姆去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.17,0:06:12.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子这场战争要输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵似乎也下定决心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.92,0:06:21.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人的武运终于到头了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过从君主会议的表决岀来的那一刻起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就已经料到这一天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐这个宫殿的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法逃离诺尔德的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.19,0:06:31.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要乘上小船逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不  就只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们平等地爱着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到最后也要平等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.45,0:06:47.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你们我就活不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子们就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不着陪着我送死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.07,0:07:20.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能成为最后一个站在阿尔图克伯爵维拉尔身边的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就得偿所愿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.33,0:07:36.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是很希望你获得幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我看上去很不幸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.26,0:07:49.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直畏惧着爱情这东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.64,0:07:56.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 事到如今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以宽恕自己了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,生命这东西就是拿来搏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用别的东西搏多好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.21,0:08:17.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言那些东西都不值一提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.13,0:08:22.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 真够疯狂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有太阳就能用它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克的船损伤严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该我们顶上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,海浪啊翻滚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰啊 炸裂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰啊  炸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德 吉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.75,0:10:22.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到瓦尔林德居然会发动这么猛烈的攻势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.34,0:10:27.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克伯爵都打击到同盟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.26,0:10:29.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们却白白浪赛时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给了对方反击的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.59,0:10:35.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而阿尔图克伯爵最先陷入了困境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是自作自受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.52,0:10:42.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜拒绝和谈是因为无法原谅阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  反过来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,她恨的只有维拉尔・康斯坦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,貝要夺走他的圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必就会接受与我方和谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你手握这样的秘密条约？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真无礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拯救阿尔图克伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为此需要承认克莱榭家为皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.05,0:11:15.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让联合的所有君主发誓为其效忠  各位意下如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是要投降吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这也是无奈之举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.10,0:11:23.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您的这份心很伟大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.56,0:11:27.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  同盟的架势就是要用战争毁灭联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论给出怎样的条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.74,0:11:31.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都无法颠覆这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.36,0:11:35.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  无论如何都要把阿尔图克伯爵救出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.87,0:11:38.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,独角兽城已被包围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.37,0:11:45.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在下认为应该讨论一下没有阿尔图克伯爵之后该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是否来得及还不好说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要从北方进攻同盟领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要后方受到威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,或许瓦尔林德就会撤军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  啊  马丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.40,0:12:08.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的结婚为的是终结混沌时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以及让大陆恢复和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这话不是你告诉我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.87,0:12:20.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,莫怕一步也别给我后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.46,0:12:29.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.67,0:12:32.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一口气攻破城门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诺尔德的士兵似乎登陆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,突破临海一侧的城墙杀到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.69,0:12:55.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也只是时间的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令过城墙的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们到时候就撤退然后回来防守城内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.79,0:13:07.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了那就开始最后一次大闹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.18,0:13:19.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,业火的玛格丽最后的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们见识一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经畏惧着爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为不愿失去所爱之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.40,0:14:14.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你将至高无上的爱献给了这样一个我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:19.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是单纯想陪在您身边而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为君主在这边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.94,0:14:55.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是诺尔德公爵埃里克的女儿 乌尔莉卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.73,0:14:56.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.28,0:15:00.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克伯爵维拉尔大人的契约魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,科林・梅萨拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,公爵还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.33,0:15:08.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你跟他的契约还有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.29,0:15:11.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.58,0:15:15.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会违反协定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.38,0:16:39.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,由我瓦尔林德军来杀死阿尔图克伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他是康斯坦斯祖父尤根的仇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,近卫队长 架好重弩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,装填圣印弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.11,0:16:59.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,第二轮射击准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.62,0:17:17.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:35.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.69,0:17:47.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就把克莱榭家的血脉和我的圣印让给你好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.66,0:17:49.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.99,0:17:54.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你尽管在自己坚信的道路上前进便是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.66,0:18:01.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过请允许我祈祷你和阿莱克希斯大人能够结合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.38,0:18:07.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我认为这才是你真正的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我的表哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.11,0:18:28.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经舍弃了自己的幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是为了告慰维拉尔大人的在天之灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.27,0:18:59.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也要尽可能地多杀敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.89,0:19:45.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是阿尔图克伯爵维拉尔•康斯坦斯的契约魔法师长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.19,0:19:47.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,劳拉・哈德利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.82,0:19:52.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城和王座就交给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.91,0:19:57.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这不意味着阿尔图克败北了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必各地的领主会向你发起反抗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,愿阿尔图克荣光常在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是海尔格・皮埃罗萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.31,0:20:24.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能否允许我继续治疗伤者呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边的伤者只要送到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会平等对待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.69,0:20:30.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城和维拉尔的圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就让给米尔扎阁下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能平定阿尔图克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有野心之人退场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.66,0:21:19.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小之人毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的时代终于来临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.75,0:21:35.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,劳拉大人在通信中让我转达维拉尔大人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.39,0:21:42.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧你给了我不少乐趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.97,0:21:48.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后请左右世界吧
